category: Web Perl
requires: apache2-mod_apreq2 apache2-mod_perl libapr1 libaprutil1 libapreq2_3 libgcc1 libssp0 perl
external-source: libapreq2
sdesc: "Apache 2 client request library (Perl bindings)"
ldesc: "libapreq is a safe, standards-compliant, high-performance 
library used for parsing HTTP cookies, query-strings and POST data. The 
perl APIs Apache::Request and Apache::Cookie are the lightweight 
mod_perl analogs of the CGI and CGI::Cookie perl modules."
